<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أخرجه الطحاوي <span class="c2">(١٢١٦)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٥ - محمد بن جُحادة الكوفي.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أخرجه الطبراني <span class="c2">(١٧/ ٢٥٥)</span> وفي <span class="c1">"لأوسط"</span> <span class="c2">(٥٩٩٦)</span> وفي <span class="c1">"الصغير"</span> <span class="c2">(٨٦٥)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
